<p class="">I have already said to the right hon. Gentleman that I cannot add any more today, and that must be my answer to the hon. Gentleman.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ed91412e-0d66-4680-98dc-fd476b839783" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
