<p class=""><em>rose</em>—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f2d1ebf3-4369-4ecb-94b7-fd6abae5f5e2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-07-29/debates/a6f0ce6e-6630-4a1b-9182-6a4d01dcfeac/EconomicPosition#contribution-f2d1ebf3-4369-4ecb-94b7-fd6abae5f5e2">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
