    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The right hon. Gentleman can say that this is nonsense, but I am expressing my view—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-74769fbb-500d-46a3-a55e-94ed990495de" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-07-29/debates/a6f0ce6e-6630-4a1b-9182-6a4d01dcfeac/EconomicPosition#contribution-74769fbb-500d-46a3-a55e-94ed990495de">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
