<p class="">I had better finish my point first. The system of controls is one which rations scarcity. Freedom would produce plenty. We have heard much about fair shares. I believe a man who works harder ought to be able to eat better. We want fair shares, not equal shares.<p></p> I congratulate my right hon. Friend the Minister of Housing and Local Government upon his succes with the housing programme, which seems to be embarrassing the Government's expenditure figures.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
