        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1e3b4616-5d8e-40f3-bb3d-15aa33240e9f">
                Mr. Roy Jenkins  (Birmingham, Stechford)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1e3b4616-5d8e-40f3-bb3d-15aa33240e9f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-07-29/debates/a6f0ce6e-6630-4a1b-9182-6a4d01dcfeac/EconomicPosition#contribution-1e3b4616-5d8e-40f3-bb3d-15aa33240e9f">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The right hon. Gentleman says he does not favour convertibility at a fixed rate. Presumably he says that it will work more advantageously at a floating <span id="1323" class="column-number" data-column-number="1323"></span> rate. That can only mean that it would work if the £ were depreciated below 2.80 dollars. A floating rate instead of a fixed rate in turn means less favourable terms of trade than at the present time. Is the right hon. Gentleman, therefore, willing to pay as a price for convertibility less favourable terms of trade in the near future?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1e3b4616-5d8e-40f3-bb3d-15aa33240e9f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-07-29/debates/a6f0ce6e-6630-4a1b-9182-6a4d01dcfeac/EconomicPosition#contribution-1e3b4616-5d8e-40f3-bb3d-15aa33240e9f">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
